title: THE ORDER Ending Explained!
author: Think Story
comment: I have to say that I hate the ending. Why do they have to forget everything? The ending was perfect, but than they had to forget everything
I think the ending was a weak ending. It destroyed character and plot development in turn for increasing curiosity. It didn’t need that big of a plot twist.
Anyone watch this video purely to see people's reactions to the ending?
Can't stand how they all lose their memory. Kind of ruined it for me tbh.
description:
We take a look at Netflix's "The Order" and talk about that twist of an ending!
